document.title: Circuit Breaker
document.description: Maintenance activities for Circuit Breaker in COMPONENT system

body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation

2. Cap. Measurement

2. Trip Circuit

## Activities

1. Moist. Content
2. Dielec. Strength
3. Acidity

## Activities

3. Func. Sequence
4. Oil Quality

document.description: Maintenance activities for Contactor in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Contactor

## Activities

1. Pickup-Dropout
2. Contact Resist.
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Mech. Endurance

# Current Transformer

## Activities

1. Ratio
2. Polarity Verif.
3. Burden
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

2. Ins. Resist.

4. Polarization

# General

## Activities

1. Sec. Injection
2. Pri. Injection
3. Settings Verif.
4. Communication
5. Contact Resist.

document.description: Maintenance activities for Motor Prot. in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Motor Prot.

## Activities

1. Starting Time
2. Stall Prot.
3. Thermal OL
4. Unbal./Ph Loss

body.raw:
# Voltage Transformer

## Activities

1. Ratio
2. Polarity Verif.
3. Burden
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

## Activities

1. Capacity Discharge
2. Voltage Stability
3. Float-Charge Efficiency
4. Ground Fault Detection

# ACB

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Trip Unit Cal.

## Activities

1. Cap. Measurement
2. Harm. Dist. Analysis
3. Switch. Transient
4. Ins. Resist.

## Activities

2. Cont. Equip. Bonding

document.title: Motor Control Center
document.description: Maintenance activities for Motor Control Center in LV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Motor Control Center

## Activities

1. Starter Cont. Op.
2. OL Relay Cal.
3. Phase Loss Det.

# UPS

## Activities

1. Battery Capacity
2. Trans. Time Grid-Batt.
3. Out. Volt. Stability

document.description: Maintenance activities for Circuit Breaker in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation

body.raw:
# Differential

## Activities

1. Rat/Ph Angle
2. Slope Char.
3. Harm. Restr.
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Functional

## Activities

1. Discrimination
2. Pickup
3. Timing

body.raw:
# Lockout Relay

## Activities

1. Func. Trip-Reset
2. Contact Resist.
3. Coil Pickup

2. Ins. Resist.
3. Mech. Operation

body.raw:
# Motor Prot.

## Activities

1. Starting Time
2. Stall Prot.
3. Thermal OL
4. Unbal./Ph Loss

# Overcurrent

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Char. Curve
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Burden

## Activities

1. Alarm Indic.
2. Trip Circuit
3. Volt. Regulation

document.title: Cooling System
document.description: Maintenance activities for Cooling System in POWER TRAFO system

body.raw:
# Cooling System

## Activities

1. Pump-Fan Op.
2. Oil Flow Verif.
3. Temp. Control

document.title: Oil Management
document.description: Maintenance activities for Oil Management in POWER TRAFO system

body.raw:
# Oil Management

## Activities

1. Moist. Content
2. Dielec. Strength
3. Acidity

document.title: Power Transformer
document.description: Maintenance activities for Power Transformer in POWER TRAFO system

body.raw:
# Power Transformer

## Activities

1. Ins. Resist.
2. Wind. Resist.
3. Turns Ratio
4. Mag. Current
5. Dielec. Absorp.
6. Diss. Gas Analysis
7. Sweep Freq. Resp.

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Op.
3. Func. Sequence
4. Oil Quality

## Activities

1. Ratio/Phase Angle
2. Slope Characteristic
3. Harmonic Restraint
4. Insulation Resistance

document.title: Main Unit
document.description: Maintenance activities for Main Unit in RMU system

body.raw:
# Main Unit

## Activities

1. Insulation Resistance
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Contact Resistance
4. Gas Pressure
5. Functional Interlock

# Starting Time

This is the documentation page for **Starting Time** which is part of the **Motor Prot.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Starting Time here.

## Procedure

1. Step one of the Starting Time procedure
2. Step two of the Starting Time procedure
3. Step three of the Starting Time procedure

## Parameters

| Parameter | Description | Default Value |
|-----------|-------------|---------------|
| Parameter 1 | Description of parameter 1 | Default value |
| Parameter 2 | Description of parameter 2 | Default value |

## Notes

Additional notes about Starting Time can be added here.

## Related Activities

- Other related activities from Motor Prot.

# Thermal OL

This is the documentation page for **Thermal OL** which is part of the **Motor Prot.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Thermal OL here.

## Procedure

1. Step one of the Thermal OL procedure
2. Step two of the Thermal OL procedure
3. Step three of the Thermal OL procedure

## Parameters

| Parameter | Description | Default Value |
|-----------|-------------|---------------|
| Parameter 1 | Description of parameter 1 | Default value |
| Parameter 2 | Description of parameter 2 | Default value |

## Notes

Additional notes about Thermal OL can be added here.

## Related Activities

- Other related activities from Motor Prot.

# Change Rate

This is the documentation page for **Change Rate** which is part of the **Underfreq.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Change Rate here.

## Procedure

# Timing

This is the documentation page for **Timing** which is part of the **Underfreq.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Timing here.

## Procedure

1. Step one of the Timing procedure
2. Step two of the Timing procedure
3. Step three of the Timing procedure

## Parameters

| Parameter | Description | Default Value |
|-----------|-------------|---------------|
| Parameter 1 | Description of parameter 1 | Default value |
| Parameter 2 | Description of parameter 2 | Default value |

## Notes

Additional notes about Timing can be added here.

## Related Activities

# Timing

This is the documentation page for **Timing** which is part of the **Undervolt.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of Timing here.

## Procedure

1. Step one of the Timing procedure
2. Step two of the Timing procedure
3. Step three of the Timing procedure

## Parameters

| Parameter | Description | Default Value |
|-----------|-------------|---------------|
| Parameter 1 | Description of parameter 1 | Default value |
| Parameter 2 | Description of parameter 2 | Default value |

## Notes

Additional notes about Timing can be added here.

## Related Activities

# CT Polarity

This is the documentation page for **CT Polarity** which is part of the **Trafo Diff.** subcategory in the **Relay** section.

## Overview

Add a brief overview of CT Polarity here.

## Procedure

1. Step one of the CT Polarity procedure
2. Step two of the CT Polarity procedure
3. Step three of the CT Polarity procedure

## Parameters

| Parameter 2 | Description of parameter 2 | Default value |

## Notes

Additional notes about CT Polarity can be added here.
